sequenceDiagram
    actor Dev as Разработчик
    participant GIT as Bitbucket Server<br/>(Git repo)
    participant PIPE as Bitbucket Pipelines<br/>(Runner)
    participant MVN as Maven<br/>(build + test)
    participant DOCKER as Docker<br/>(build + push)
    participant REG as Docker Registry<br/>:5000
    participant HELM as Helm
    participant K8S as Kubernetes<br/>(Timeweb Cloud)
    participant APP as greeting-service<br/>pod

    Dev->>GIT: git push origin develop

    GIT->>PIPE: webhook: new commit on develop

    Note over PIPE: Шаг 1 — Build & Test
    PIPE->>MVN: mvn clean verify -B
    MVN-->>PIPE: ✅ тесты прошли, JAR собран

    Note over PIPE: Шаг 2 — Docker Build & Push
    PIPE->>DOCKER: docker build -t registry/greeting-service:abc12345 .
    DOCKER-->>PIPE: ✅ image собран
    PIPE->>REG: docker push registry/greeting-service:abc12345
    REG-->>PIPE: ✅ image загружен

    Note over PIPE: Шаг 3 — Deploy to Dev
    PIPE->>HELM: helm upgrade --install greeting-service<br/>--set image.tag=abc12345<br/>--namespace dev --atomic
    HELM->>K8S: apply Deployment, Service, Ingress
    K8S->>REG: imagePull: greeting-service:abc12345
    REG-->>K8S: ✅ image получен
    K8S->>APP: запуск нового пода
    APP-->>K8S: /actuator/health/readiness → UP
    K8S-->>HELM: ✅ rollout complete
    HELM-->>PIPE: ✅ deploy success

    Note over PIPE: Шаг 4 — Post-deploy check
    PIPE->>K8S: kubectl rollout status deployment/...
    K8S-->>PIPE: ✅ deployment rolled out
    PIPE->>APP: curl http://ingress-ip/api/greeting
    APP-->>PIPE: 200 OK {"message": "Hello, World!"}

    PIPE-->>Dev: ✅ Pipeline SUCCESS — commit abc12345 задеплоен в dev

    Note over Dev,K8S: Деплой в prod — ручное подтверждение в UI Bitbucket
    Dev->>PIPE: ▶️ Ручной запуск "Deploy to Production"
    PIPE->>HELM: helm upgrade --install greeting-service<br/>--namespace prod --atomic --timeout 10m
    HELM->>K8S: rolling update (maxSurge=1, maxUnavailable=0)
    K8S-->>HELM: ✅ all pods ready
    PIPE-->>Dev: ✅ Production deploy SUCCESS
